text: The All-Ukrainian Political Party "Ecology and Social Protection" () is a political party in Ukraine registered in November 2003. „Всеукраїнська Політична партія – Екологія та Соціальний захист“, Database DATA The party did not participate in national elections till 2007. In the 2007 parliamentary elections, the party failed as part of the Christian Bloc to win parliamentary representation. The party did not participate in the 2012 parliamentary elections. Results of voting in single constituencies in 2012 & Nation-wide list , Central Election Commission of Ukraine And again the party did not participate in the 2014 Ukrainian parliamentary election.Alphabetical Index of parties in 2014 Ukrainian parliamentary election , Central Election Commission of Ukraine ==References== Category:Political parties in Ukraine
